<plot>Pablo is a Bible-quoting hit-man who works along side of his wise-cracking sidekick Pedro. The dual relish in there work and even offer there victims the opportunity to redeem themselves before terminating their life. Conflict occurs when Pablo is asked to kill a local pastor whose community outreach is curtailing the neighborhood dug trade. The security of his family, his friendship to Pedro and his own life are threatened when Pablo has second thoughts about killing a Reverend.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?168679</url></doc>
